citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:00 am on 18-
AUG-2022. The attempt was made during licensees stated "Optimal Hours". A responsible adult shall be made available
to accompany USDA, APHIS Officials during unannounced inspections.
End Section
